  <brief_title>Metformin in Patients With PCOS and Predictors of Poor Ovarian Response Ongoing In-vitro Fertilization</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Metformin on the Ovarian Response to Gonadotropins for in Vitro Fertilization Treatment in Patients With Polycystic Ovary Syndrome and Predictors of Poor Ovarian Response</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
